  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        -  Diabetic glucose pattern by oral glucose tolerance test (OGTT) of &gt;200 at 120 min.
             (stable and healthy at time of OGTT)

          -  Fasting glucose levels &lt;126.

          -  Weight stable within 5% in previous 3 months.

          -  Free from illness for two months.

          -  Male and female 16 and older, who are done growing

          -  Willing to come in for visits every 3 months.

          -  Patients receiving infrequent short bursts of systemic glucocorticoids may be
             considered for the study inclusion if: a. they have not received systemic
             glucocorticoids steroids for at least one month, b. they did not receive the steroids
             for more than 14 consecutive days or 28 days total in six months
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
